Brazil High Interest Rates May Discourage Investment, Valor Says

-- B y   I u r i   D a n t a s
-- 
2011-06-06T13:19:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/brazil-high-interest-rates-may-discourage-investment-valor-says.html
Brazil ’s real interest rates may make
it difficult to sustain the rate of investment in the economy,
Valor Economico  said , citing an interview with Marcio Holland,
economic policy secretary at the  Finance Ministry .  The central bank and Finance Ministry’s measures to curb
 consumer credit  succeeded in the first quarter, the Sao Paulo-
based newspaper cited Holland as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
